videos.description: Troy quarterback Sawyer Smith launches a 49-yard pass to Damion Willis, then finds Deondre Douglas in the end zone for a 23-yard touchdown vs. Liberty.
videos.headline: Troy completes back-to-back big plays for TD

videos.description: Liberty quarterback Stephen Calvert runs the play action and airs it out to Khaleb Coleman in the end zone for a 29-yard touchdown to even the score vs. Troy.
videos.headline: Liberty scores 29-yard TD on play-action pass

videos.description: Peytton Pickett takes the handoff and gets into the end zone from 2 yards out to take the lead over Troy.
videos.headline: Pickett plows it in for Liberty TD

videos.description: The Liberty Flames get tricky on a two-point conversion late in the fourth quarter vs. Troy as DJ Stubbs runs a reverse and hits B.J. Farrow in the end zone.
videos.headline: Liberty runs version of 'Philly Special' on 2-point conversion
